# Application Overview - ElectricalDiagramAnalyzer

## Purpose

The **ElectricalDiagramAnalyzer** is a PDF analysis system that:
1. Extracts electrical panel schedules from PDF drawings
2. Uses OCR to read breaker configurations
3. Applies business rules to generate Square D part numbers
4. Returns structured data for downstream ordering systems

